query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS projectModels3D (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  projectId INT NOT NULL,
  modelId INT NOT NULL,
  location VARCHAR(255),
  notes TEXT,
  addedById INT NOT NULL,
  addedAt TIMESTAMP NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  FOREIGN KEY (projectId) REFERENCES projects(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
  FOREIGN KEY (modelId) REFERENCES library3DModels(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
  FOREIGN KEY (addedById) REFERENCES users(id),
  INDEX projectModel_project_idx (projectId),
  INDEX projectModel_model_idx (modelId)
);
